SUMMARY:Decadent 80s Dance Party featuring DJ NoN
DESCRIPTION:Get ready for a fun night of dancing to all your favorite hits and requests from the 1980s! \nD80s is Portland’s longest-running 80s night\, celebrating 21 consecutive years of weekly events. It’s the official 80s night for Goonies Weekend in Astoria and hosts special events at select venues throughout Portland and across Oregon. \nFans of 80s alternative music will feel right at home-D80s takes requests seriously while keeping each set fresh and dynamic week after week. \nStop by and discover why D80s is Portland’s go-to 80s club dance night.
URL:https://www.crystalballroompdx.com/events/274884-decadent-80s-dance-party-featuring-dj-non/
CATEGORIES:March
